title: [Patreon Preview] Barbara and Lottie
itunes:title: [Patreon Preview] Barbara and Lottie
description:
This week, Jim introduces everyone to his and his brother's alter egos, Barbara and Lottie, Jack makes everyone guess Beatles lyrics, which Forrest thinks is a great idea, and they talk about how traveling and car rental companies are the worst while dramatic music plays in the background.
